== 开发 ==
[[File:Backtothefuture-telltalegame-characters.jpg|thumb]]

2010年6月初，作为创作改编自[[环球影业|环球影业]]《[[回到未来系列|回到未来]]》和《[[侏罗纪公园|侏罗纪公园]]》系列电影的电子游戏的许可权交易的一份子，Telltale Games公布了《回到未来：游戏版》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/nbcuni |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vIBSVx08?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/nbcuni |archivedate=2010-12-27 |title=Telltale Games and NBC Universal Announce Multi-Title Video Game Development Deal |date=2010-06-09 |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |accessdate=2010-11-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/109/1095895p1.html |title=Telltale Going Back to the Future |author=Reilly, Jim |date=2010-06-09 |work=IGN.com |publisher=IGN Entertainment, Inc. |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2012-07-06 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68wqiIUib?url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/109/1095895p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。作品被分成五个章节在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[OS_X|OS X]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]、[[Wii|Wii]]（单独零售版）和[[iOS|iOS]]平台发布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/company/pressreleases/id-117 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vIdsLkPf?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/company/pressreleases/id-117 |archivedate=2010-12-27 |title=Great Scott! Back to the Future: The Game Platforms Announced and Pre-Orders Begin |date=2010-10-25 |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |accessdate=2010-12-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

开发团队透过网上调查寻求影迷们在各种场合下的选择<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/215763/telltale-games-asks-fans-for-feedback-on-back-to-the-future-game-ideas-and-bttf-fanboy-dave-gives-his/ |title=Telltale Games asks fans for feedback on Back to the Future game ideas and BTTF fanboy Dave gives his |author=Rudden, Dave |date=2010-07-08 |work=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |publisher=GamePro Media, Inc. |accessdate=2010-10-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101112095357/http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/215763/telltale-games-asks-fans-for-feedback-on-back-to-the-future-game-ideas-and-bttf-fanboy-dave-gives-his/ |archivedate=2010-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，并邀请电影三部曲的联合创作人、联合编剧和联合制片人{{le|鲍勃·盖尔|Bob Gale}}担任剧情顾问<ref>{{cite web |url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/08/telltale-games-times-back-to-the-future-project/1 |title=Telltale Games times 'Back to the Future' project |author=Snider, Mike |date=2010-09-01 |work=USA Today |publisher=Gannett Co. Inc. |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2012-08-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69n7mcU1N?url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2010/08/telltale-games-times-back-to-the-future-project/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="concept">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-660 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vIGaySqc?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-660 |archivedate=2010-12-27 |title=Great Scott! Doc Brown and Marty Are Headed Back to the Future...Again |author=Johnson, Alan |date=2010-09-01 |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |accessdate=2010-12-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。鲍勃和导演[[罗伯特·泽米吉斯|罗伯特·泽米吉斯]]提出[[回到未来II|第二部电影]]中的原本概念，如探索公约时代和博士的家族史，都被修改成游戏<ref name="galeqa">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-687 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vIJAusGZ?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-687 |archivedate=2010-12-27 |title=Bob Gale Answers Your Back to the Future Questions |author=Johnson, Alan |date=2010-10-18 |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |accessdate=2010-10-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。Telltale Games秉承电影所设立的时间线成为剧本开发方面的最大挑战之一<ref name="script">{{cite web |url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/111/1118473p1.html |title=Doc Brown Speaks Up at PAX |author=Buchanan, Levi |date=2010-09-04 |work=IGN.com |publisher=IGN Entertainment, Inc. |accessdate=2010-10-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100909014201/http://pc.ign.com/articles/111/1118473p1.html |archivedate=2010-09-09 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。许多造成与电影剧情矛盾的构思因冲突而被废弃<ref name="script" />。盖尔表示，尽管游戏并不是系列电影的正典<ref name="galeqa" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/10/25/back-to-the-future-bob-gale-interview/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vMU3pD26?url=http://blog.moviefone.com/2010/10/25/back-to-the-future-bob-gale-interview/ |archivedate=2010-12-30 |title='Back to the Future' Co-Creator Bob Gale on the New Blu-ray, Sequels and Why People Don't Like Part Three |author=Davis, Erik |date=2010-10-25 |work=Moviefone |publisher=AOL Inc. |accessdate=2010-12-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NE1ZNmTWpbxL56 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vMU93UOu?url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/NE1ZNmTWpbxL56 |archivedate=2010-12-30 |title=Exclusive: Bob Gale Talks Back to the Future Blu-ray Trilogy |date=2010-10-26 |work=MovieWeb.com |publisher=MovieWeb, Inc. |accessdate=2010-12-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但它的剧情可能会按照[[架空历史小说|架空时间线]]发展<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a271413/back-to-the-future-game-for-november.html |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vMTwdbhW?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a271413/back-to-the-future-game-for-november.html |archivedate=2010-12-30 |title='Back To The Future' game for 'November' |author=Reynolds, Matthew; Reynolds, Simon |date=2010-09-02 |work=Digital Spy |publisher=Digital Spy Limited |accessdate=2010-12-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2010年9月，团队公布主角首张概念图。该图由艺术家{{le|莱恩·琼斯|Ryan Jones}}根据[[迈克尔·J·福克斯|迈克尔·J·福克斯]]和[[克里斯托弗·劳埃德|克里斯托弗·劳埃德]]的外形塑造<ref name="concept" />。总设计师和编剧[[迈克尔·施特穆勒|迈克尔·施特穆勒]]强调游戏的图形会不太逼真，方法更加风格化，以营造出忠于三部曲的感觉<ref name="ignstemmle">{{cite web |url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/113/1136346p1.html |title=Back to the Future: Your First Look |author=Onyett, Charles |date=2010-11-23 |work=IGN.com |publisher=IGN Entertainment, Inc. |accessdate=2010-11-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101206014709/http://pc.ign.com/articles/113/1136346p1.html |archivedate=2010-12-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。谜题被设计成需依靠角色的物品清单中的可使用物件和其他开发商没有为主角马蒂考虑、各个部分能组装成小工具的物件<ref name="ignstemmle" />。

由于福克斯无法为游戏出演马蒂一角，新人{{le|A·J·洛卡斯齐奥|A.J. Locascio}}将代替他为主角配音<ref name="martyvoice">{{cite web |url=http://www.gametrailers.com/video/exclusive-behind-back-to-the/706591 |title=Back to the Future: The Game - Behind the Scenes Part 2: Hey McFly! |date=2010-10-23 |work=GameTrailers.com |publisher=MTV Networks |accessdate=2010-10-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026064802/http://www.gametrailers.com/video/exclusive-behind-back-to-the/706591 |archivedate=2010-10-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但福克斯后来在第五章中为马蒂的祖父威廉，以及三个出现在游戏结尾镜头中的未来主义版本马蒂提供配音<ref name="surprisevoice">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-828 |title=Review: Back to the Future: Behind The Scenes - Special Surprise Voice Joins the Cast! |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |date=2011-06-03 |accessdate=2011-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013190907/http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-828 |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="ep5 date fox" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5808582/michael-j-fox-returns-for-back-to-the-futures-final-episode|title=Michael J. Fox Returns for Back to the Future’s Final Episode|last=Good|first=Owen|publisher=Kotaku|date=2011-06-04|accessdate=2011-06-04|archive-date=2011-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607033217/http://kotaku.com/5808582/michael-j-fox-returns-for-back-to-the-futures-final-episode|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洛卡斯齐奥为了赢得这一角色，向配音导演朱利安·科瓦内斯基（{{lang|en|Julian Kwasneski}}）寄去试音样本的电子邮件，设法打动盖尔和劳埃德，让两人发现他的声线非常接近福克斯在拍摄三部曲时的声音<ref name="martyvoice" />。劳埃德回归为布朗博士配音，并于2010年9月下旬启动了他的首轮录音<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-673 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vIZe3aSg?url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-673 |archivedate=2010-12-27 |title=The Doctor Is In: Christopher Lloyd Begins Doc Brown Voice Work |author=Johnson, Alan |date=2010-09-21 |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |accessdate=2010-10-17 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。后来，{{le|克劳迪娅·威尔斯|Claudia Wells}}加盟团队，再次演绎珍妮·帕克（{{lang|en|Jennifer Parker}}）一角<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/25/claudia-wells-reprises-her-role-as-jennifer-in-back-to-the-futures-third-episode/ | title = Claudia Wells reprises her role as Jennifer in Back to the Future’s third episode | publisher = VG247 | date = 2011-03-25 | accessdate = 2011-03-25 | first = Stephany | last = Nunneley | archive-date = 2012-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120707090110/http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/25/claudia-wells-reprises-her-role-as-jennifer-in-back-to-the-futures-third-episode/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。基德·彼洋代替演员[[托马斯·弗朗西斯·威尔逊|托马斯·弗朗西斯·威尔逊]]为比夫·塔内（{{lang|en|Biff Tannen}}）配音<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-798 |title=Kid Beyond Speaks - A Video Chat |publisher=Telltale, Incorporated |date=2011-04-22 |accessdate=2011-07-21 |first=Alan |last=Johnson |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014024924/http://www.telltalegames.com/community/blogs/id-798 |archivedate=2012-10-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，{{le|詹姆斯·阿诺德·泰勒|James Arnold Taylor}}为年轻的爱默配音<ref>{{cite web|url= http://moviemikes.com/2011/02/interview-with-james-arnold-taylor/|title= Interview with James Arnold Taylor|publisher= Movie Mikes|date= 2011-02-11|accessdate= 2011-07-21|first= Mike|last= Gencarelli|archive-date= 2011-02-16|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110216213447/http://moviemikes.com/2011/02/interview-with-james-arnold-taylor/|dead-url= no}}</ref>。尽管乔治、洛林·麦佛莱等角色在游戏中回归，但这些角色配音工作由湾区的可配音演员完成。汤姆·威尔逊在30周年重制版中为比夫·塔内配音<ref>{{cite web|last1=Nunneley|first1=Stephany|title=Telltale releasing Back to the Future: The Game – 30th Anniversary Edition on PS4, Xbox One|url=https://www.vg247.com/2015/09/29/back-to-the-future-the-game-30th-anniversary-ps4-xbox-one/|website=VG247|accessdate=2015-10-02|date=2015-09-29|archive-date=2015-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150930210151/http://www.vg247.com/2015/09/29/back-to-the-future-the-game-30th-anniversar