== 宣传 ==
[[File:Ttg_delorean_pax.jpg|thumb]]

为了宣传游戏，游戏公布后不久，Telltale在2010年的{{le|彭妮通道游戏博览会|Penny Arcade Expo}}的展台上展出了德罗宁时间机器的复制品<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.destructoid.com/telltale-games-is-bringing-a-delorean-time-machine-to-pax-182573.phtml|title= Telltale Games is bringing a DeLorean time machine to PAX|first= Jordan|last= Devore|date= 2010-09-27|accessdate= 2010-10-23|publisher= Destructoid|archive-date= 2012-08-09|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/69n7pHVrF?url=http://www.destructoid.com/telltale-games-is-bringing-a-delorean-time-machine-to-pax-182573.phtml|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20015625-1.html|title= PAX day 1: Torchlight II, Goldeneye 007, Tron|publisher= CNet|first= Matt|last= Hickey|date= 2010-09-04|accessdate= 2010-10-23|archive-date= 2012-08-09|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/69n7qXECy?url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-20015625-1.html|dead-url= no}}</ref>。游戏发行前夕，Telltale Games发表他们的第一部[[Facebook|Facebook]]游戏《回到未来：穿越时空的闪电战》（{{lang|en|Back to the Future: Blitz Through Time}}），其玩法类似于《{{le|宝石迷阵闪电风暴|Bejeweled Blitz}}》并配以游戏情节<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/217282/back-to-the-future-puzzle-game-on-facebook/ | title = Back to the Future puzzle game on Facebook | first = Dave | last = Rudden | date = 2010-11-15 | accessdate = 2010-11-15 | publisher = [[GamePro|GamePro]] | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/217282/back-to-the-future-puzzle-game-on-facebook/&date=2011-11-30+19:01:57 | archivedate = 2011-11-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/11/15/telltale-releases-free-match-three-back-to-the-future-puzzle-gam/|title=Telltale releases free match-three Back to the Future puzzle game on Facebook|first=Mike|last=Schramm|publisher=Joystiq|date=2010-11-15|accessdate=2010-11-24|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66nGmPr6d?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/11/15/telltale-releases-free-match-three-back-to-the-future-puzzle-gam/|archive-date=2012-04-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。游戏到2012年已下架。

2010年10月26日，游戏第一章免费拷贝的优惠券公布，附带电影上映25周年蓝光纪念版<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.1up.com/news/future-blu-ray-includes-voucher-telltale|title= Back to the Future Blu-ray Includes Voucher for Free Episode of Telltale Game|publisher= 1UP.com|date= 2010-10-18|accessdate= 2010-10-23|first= Kat|last= Bailey|archive-date= 2012-08-09|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/69n7raZbg?url=http://www.1up.com/news/future-blu-ray-includes-voucher-telltale|dead-url= no}}</ref>。Telltale网站制作的促销广告连接到免费拷贝<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |title=Telltale Games |date=2010-10-25 |publisher=[[Telltale_Games|Telltale Games]] |accessdate=2010-10-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101116042601/http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |archivedate=2010-11-16 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。尽管有促销活动，第一章于2011年2月16日发行<ref name="bttfoffer3rdrevision">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |title=Telltale Games - ''Back to the Future: The Game'' – The Adventure Begins! |date=2010-12 |publisher=[[Telltale_Games|Telltale Games]] |accessdate=2010-12-23 |quote=Free episodes distribution begins in February, as the second episode releases. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110101041447/http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |archivedate=2011-01-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。截至2011年4月，Telltale为网站所有注册账户免费提供第一章<ref>{{cite web | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/get-the-first-episode-of-back-to-the-future-game-for-free/1 | title = Get the first episode of 'Back to the Future' game for free | first = Brett | last = Molina | date = 2011-04-01 | accessdate = 2011-04-01 | work = USA Today | archive-date = 2011-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110407100823/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/get-the-first-episode-of-back-to-the-future-game-for-free/1 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。作为预购的奖励，Telltale向订购者提供《{{le|谜题侦探|Puzzle Agent}}》的免费拷贝和访问网站预发行内部论坛的权限。公司还表示代表每位买主向{{le|迈克尔·J·福克斯帕金森病研究基金会|The Michael J. Fox Foundation}}捐献一美元<ref>{{cite web |title=Where Back to the Future: The Game's going, we won't need Wiimotes |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/10/25/back-to-the-future-the-game-on-pc-mac-ps3-ipad/ |publisher=Joystiq |author=McElroy, Griffin |date=2010-10-25 |accessdate=2010-10-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030005455/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/10/25/back-to-the-future-the-game-on-pc-mac-ps3-ipad/ |archivedate=2010-10-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="bttfoffernew">{{cite web |url=http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |title=Telltale Games – Great Scott! |date=2010-10 |publisher=[[Telltale_Games|Telltale Games]] |accessdate=2010-11-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101019234412/http://www.telltalegames.com/bttfoffer |archivedate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

