游戏获得普遍积极的评价。第一章《该上路了》被多位评论家称赞为系列的有效开头。[[IGN|IGN]]的格雷格·米勒（{{lang|en|Greg Miller}}）给予本章8.5/10分，并写道，“这是一部电影风格的游戏，但他没有被原著吸住，反而把角色推进有意思的方向，鞭打出一个好故事。”米勒赞赏Telltale Games用注重细节和反复的风趣对话重现《回到未来》的宇宙<ref name="ign">{{cite web|url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/114/1141725p1.html|title=Back to the Future Review - PC Review|publisher=[[IGN.com|IGN.com]]|first=Greg|last=Miller|date=2010-12-23|accessdate=2011-01-04|archive-date=2012-07-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69AADQG7Y?url=http://pc.ign.com/articles/114/1141725p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Gamespot|Gamespot]]的内森·穆尼耶（{{lang|en|Nathan Meunier}}）给予本章7.5/10分，称该系列“展示了其作为处女作的许多承诺”。评论补充道，“有趣的故事紧接着被可靠的角色互动增强，将伟大意义上的真实感灌输到冒险中。”穆尼耶还注意到作品“在挑战和内容上散发出令人惊讶的光芒”<ref name="gamespot">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/pc/action/backtothefuture/review.html |title=Back to the Future: The Game - Episode 1 Review for PC |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |publisher=CBS Interactive |first=Nathan |last=Meunier |date=2011-01-03 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110930004028/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/action/backtothefuture/review.html |archivedate=2011-09-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[GameZone|GameZone]]的本·佩尔李（{{lang|en|Ben PerLee}}）总结称，他称赞了游戏，表示这“对每一位《回到未来》的影迷来说，都是自我感觉良好的电影体验，其他人都应该好好看看<ref name="gamezone review">{{cite web |url=http://pc.gamezone.com/reviews/item/back_to_the_future_the_game/ |title=Back to the Future: The Game Review |first=Ben |last=PerLee |date=2010-12-29 |accessdate=2011-01-02 |publisher=GameZone |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904063840/http://pc.gamezone.com/reviews/item/back_to_the_future_the_game |archivedate=2011-09-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{le|PALGN|PALGN}}给予作品7/10分，表示影迷“会发现所有的倒叙和怀旧时刻蕴含着大量的爱”，但称游戏的节奏慢，上世纪30年代的设定平淡。评论总结道，“影迷们会为《是时候了》更加怀旧和巧妙的时刻感到欣喜的”，但这是一个短暂、简单，开头有些平淡的游戏，我们仍然希望用时间来改善这些缺陷<ref name="palgn">{{cite web |url=http://palgn.com.au/pc-gaming/17911/back-to-the-future-the-game-episode-1-its-about-time-review/ |title=Back to the Future: The Game Episode 1: It's About Time Review |publisher=PALGN |first=Adam |last=Ghiggino |date=2010-12-23 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016063105/http://palgn.com.au/pc-gaming/17911/back-to-the-future-the-game-episode-1-its-about-time-review/ |archivedate=2012-10-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。“在一篇2/5星的评论中，《[[帝国_(杂志)|帝国]]》杂志称游戏的第一章“并未完全获得电影的基调，没能提供很多极富魅力的游戏玩法。”评论员称摄制、情况和角色“平淡”，并进一步称角色是“纸板式的无名之辈”，就没有评论系列的其他章节了<ref name="escapist">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/reviews/8495-Review-Back-to-the-Future-The-Game |title=Review: Back to the Future: The Game |work=The Escapist |publisher=Themis Group |date=2010-12-30 |accessdate=2011-01-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105093924/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/editorials/reviews/8495-Review-Back-to-the-Future-The-Game |archivedate=2011-01-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。评论家的共识是，除了配音是个例外，都特别赞赏A·J·洛卡斯齐奥模仿迈克尔·J·福克斯扮演马蒂·麦佛莱。大多数评论家都批评章节的难题是过于简单和容易的<ref name="ign" /><ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="palgn" /><ref name="escapist" />。评论聚合网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]给情节打出74/100分的平均得分<ref name="mc1" />。

截至2011年2月，游戏是Telltale Games最成功的专营权作品<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/02/18/back-to-the-future-is-telltales-most-successful-franchise/|title=''Back to the Future'' is Telltale's 'most successful' franchise|first=David|last=Hinkle|publisher=Joystiq|date=2011-02-18|accessdate=2011-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629123735/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/02/18/back-to-the-future-is-telltales-most-successful-franchise/|archive-date=2011-06-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

